# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# VEILORACLE — Environment Variables
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# Most features work WITHOUT any API keys (RSS feeds + sample data).

# NewsAPI Key (optional, free tier: https://newsapi.org)
# Without this, the system uses RSS feeds and sample data.
NEWSAPI_KEY=

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AI ENGINES — All run locally, no external API keys needed!
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 1. Sentence Embeddings (all-MiniLM-L6-v2) — auto-downloaded
# 2. DBSCAN Clustering — scikit-learn, no config needed
# 3. VADER Sentiment — nltk, auto-downloaded
# 4. NLP Preprocessing — nltk, auto-downloaded
# 5. Named Entity Recognition — spaCy en_core_web_sm, auto-downloaded
# 6. BART Summarization — transformers, auto-downloaded (optional)
# 7. Impact Prediction — rule-based, no config needed
# 8. Anomaly Detection — numpy z-score, no config needed
# 9. Trend Forecasting — numpy linear regression, no config needed
